{
  "stem": "11184.3",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 96.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Well, [LAUGHS] it's a lot to talk about.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I'm not saying-- very, very difficult life.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 123,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very difficult life.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 124,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In 1946, in Konstanz.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We went to-- we went to-- we moved into this Konstanz and Bodensee to-- you know, because it was a nice little city.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were helped by the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "They were helping us.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then we worked a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "You know, he worked a little.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was selling, you know, different things.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 125,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so--",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 126,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, he went to those little islands and bought eggs and butter and came back and say, well, always a businessman.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, I don't-- we-- just-- at the beginning, you didn't need much.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We got something from the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 127,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So you spend, and you make some profit, and that's how people were doing.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My mother was with me.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 128,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Pregnant in-- well, let's see, in '47.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "My son was born in-- let's see, November, November in '47.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 129,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I had a baby right there.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Mhm.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 130,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The oldest.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 131,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 132,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Leo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 133,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Leo.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 134,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In Konstanz, we lived-- a German woman rented a room for us, one room.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 135,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Again one room, yeah.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 136,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 137,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 138,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Just took care of the baby.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I didn't work.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Because our needs were so minimal, really.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I mean, look-- and food we got from the UNRRA.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So-- and he was making a few dollars selling things and buying, yeah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 139,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So it wasn't too bad then, after-- after the war.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It's not what I decided.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The-- the-- the Joint Distribution Committee came over and then said that they can take us.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You know, if we like to go, they will send us to the United States.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we did.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 140,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We did decide yes.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 141,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And they asked me what city?",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
